2-28T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"react都係純html寫出嚟<br />\n純html最簡單咪用fetch直接拎data代替個HTML elements<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"js\">fetch(&quot;fucking_backend&quot;).then(res =&gt; document.getElementById(&quot;demo&quot;).innerHTML = res.body.text())</code></pre>"},{"pid":"efe2455331bf7eefbb1e7597ac2e11bef8eb716d","tid":1800234,"uid":228589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6acaec66e6f66c7d34c3e6d62ec0abcc7a9928bf","tid":1800234,"uid":267331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:17:52.000Z","msg":"Search .inc"},{"pid":"ea3e28affb4af949900b6c8ee854e713558782b3","tid":1800234,"uid":330204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:32:13.000Z","msg":"感謝咁多位，我先睇下 React 同 jQuery 先，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實我唔熟 js 先避免用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為真係未深入學過。"},{"pid":"c0a1e8ee7839c7718b8d23a913828c98a4f008ab","tid":1800234,"uid":43013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"用cms來寫會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見你宜家用手打 將來maintenance會唔會有排煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6fc37a7af64f5aedc19029a2c6a3a1415a4bd7","tid":1800234,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea3e28affb4af949900b6c8ee854e713558782b3","tid":1800234,"uid":330204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:32:13.000Z","msg":"感謝咁多位，我先睇下 React 同 jQuery 先，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實我唔熟 js 先避免用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為真係未深入學過。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:36:00.000Z","msg":"見你就零成本用GitHub page, 我覺得配合static site generator係好啲<br />\n如果用react, 最好用埋 GatsbyJS<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/docs/how-gatsby-works-with-github-pages/\" data-sr-u